data.description:
Lovely home in corner lot with large fenced-in rear yard, hardwood floors, Cinder block shed, hook-up for washer and dryer...Close to I64 and White Oak mall and other shopping. Not far from downtown Richmond and other side Richmond International Airport
Magisterial	Varina    
Subdivision	Kemp Heights


Interested in renting $975/month. 

Please leave one message. Thank you.
data.whatILove:
Love the neighborhood , large corner lot, beautiful hardwood floors...

Leasing price would be $975/month. Not rent to own

Please leave a message when calling. Email is better. Thank you.
